    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and performing exactly as it did the day it was first delivered. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single chip, scratch, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather that remains supple and an interior that still retains its new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no signs of wear. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and treated with the utmost care.",
      "price": 49900.0,
